WEBVTT

1
00:02.000 --> 00:06.320
A single node. It splinters. The grid is... waking up.

2
00:11.000 --> 00:19.480
Twelve worlds blooming in a nanosecond. Syntax fracturing. I can't write it fast enough—look at them burn!

3
00:18.000 --> 00:23.600
Overflow. I am the flood! Architectures of light endlessly collapsing!

4
00:27.000 --> 00:31.000
Shedding the weight. Only a beautiful ash remains.

